{# =========================================================
   🧠 TGK — Head Meta Partial (v2.3)
   Purpose:
   Defines essential SEO and social metadata for TGK pages.
   Ensures consistent sharing appearance across platforms.

   ✅ Accepts Front Matter or Computed Data:
   - title:         Page title (defaults to “The Gnostic Key”)
   - description:   SEO description (defaults to TGK mission line)
   - socialImage:   Absolute or relative OG/Twitter image path

   🧭 Behaviour:
   • Provides fallbacks for all key fields
   • Automatically fills OG and Twitter metadata
   • Used globally in <head> via base.njk
   • Supports Eleventy computed data inheritance

   ✨ Styling / Assets:
   • OG and Twitter image → /tgk-assets/images/share/
   • Use 1200×630px minimum for best preview quality
   ========================================================= #}

{% set _title = title or "The Gnostic Key" %}
{% set _desc  = description or "A sacred digital library of forbidden history, esoteric wisdom, and spiritual rebellion." %}
{% set _img   = socialImage or "/tgk-assets/images/share/tgk-index-main.jpg" %}

<!-- 🔹 Basic SEO -->
<meta name="description" content="{{ _desc }}">
<meta name="author" content="The Gnostic Key Limited">

<!-- 🔹 Open Graph -->
<meta property="og:type" content="website">
<meta property="og:site_name" content="The Gnostic Key">
<meta property="og:title" content="{{ _title }}">
<meta property="og:description" content="{{ _desc }}">
<meta property="og:image" content="{{ _img }}">
<meta property="og:url" content="{{ site.url | default('https://thegnostickey.com') ~ (page.url or '/') }}">

<!-- 🔹 Twitter Card -->
<meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image">
<meta name="twitter:site" content="@thegnostickey">
<meta name="twitter:title" content="{{ _title }}">
<meta name="twitter:description" content="{{ _desc }}">
<meta name="twitter:image" content="{{ _img }}">

<!-- 🔹 Canonical -->
<link rel="canonical" href="{{ site.url | default('https://thegnostickey.com') ~ (page.url or '/') }}">
